  "body": "<h1>Raju Gosling – Malayalam Main Character Meme Tee</h1>\n<h3><span>For that friend who thinks he’s the hero in every scene.</span></h3>\n<p>What if all the cool, silent guys from your favourite movies merged into one Malayali main character? Raju Gosling is our crossover between Ryan Gosling’s brooding loner roles in films like Drive and Blade Runner 2049, and Prithviraj’s intense Aadhi from Ranam.<br>This tee is made for the campus “mystery guy” – the one who doesn’t talk much, walks around with headphones on, always rides alone and still somehow becomes the hero in everyone else’s story. If you’ve ever been called “Ryan Gosling of our batch” or “Prithvi of our gang”, this is literally your uniform.<br>Printed on premium 100% cotton, the Raju Gosling Tee keeps you comfortable through long college days, night rides and solo theatre visits. The relaxed unisex fit works perfectly for that low‑effort, high‑aura look – no overacting, just clean silhouette and a strong vibe.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>100% cotton, soft and breathable for all‑day wear</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Crossover design inspired by Ryan Gosling’s iconic loner characters and Prithviraj’s Aadhi in <em>Ranam</em><span data-state=\"closed\"></span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Durable print designed to handle repeated washing (no cheap peeling)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Unisex fit – works for both him, her, they &amp; them.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Perfect for college fests, birthday gifts and hostel OOTDs</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Original Petrocrib Malayalam meme design</p>\n</li>\n<li><br></li>\n</ul>",
