  "handle": "chitram",
  "title": "Chitram",
  "body": "<h1>Chitram – Cult Classic Malayalam Love Story Tee</h1>\n<h3>For everyone who still believes “old Mallu movies hit different.”</h3>\n<p>Not every favourite movie is a new release. Some stay in your heart because you grew up with them, heard the songs on TV, and still quote the scenes years later. Chitram is our tribute to one of Malayalam cinema’s most loved cult classics – a film remembered for its unforgettable love story, legendary performances and the kind of simple, emotional storytelling we rarely see now.<br>This tee is for the people who still put on old CDs, hunt for classic clips on YouTube and randomly hum the songs when they are alone. Whether you watched it in theatres back in the day or discovered it later through family, Chitram represents that one movie you can rewatch any number of times and still feel something.<br>Printed on premium 100% cotton, the Chitram Tee is a soft, everyday way to carry your favourite Malayalam love story with you – to college, café meets, movie marathons or just late‑night nostalgia sessions with friends. The relaxed unisex fit makes it easy to style while keeping all the attention on the artwork and the emotion behind it.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Tribute to a cult classic Malayalam love story</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Perfect for old‑school Mollywood fans and romance lovers</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>100% cotton – soft, breathable and ideal for daily wear</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Relaxed unisex fit – suits most body types and styles</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Durable print that keeps the artwork sharp over time</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Designed by Petrocrib for Malayalam cinema lovers</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>",
