  "handle": "sagar-alias-jacky",
  "title": "Sagar Alias Jacky",
  "body": "<h1>Sagar Alias Jacky – Mohanlal 80s Action Legend Tribute Tee</h1>\n<h3>Petrocrib × Akash (NID Ahmedabad) – Limited collab design</h3>\n<p>This isn't just another tee – it's a collector's piece. Sagar Alias Jacky celebrates Mohanlal's legendary character from Irupatham Noottandu, the 1987 action classic that defined 80s Mollywood with its raw energy, mass dialogues and Sagar's unforgettable swagger as the ultimate anti-hero.<br>What makes this special? It's a Petrocrib × Akash collaboration with Mr. Akash, a renowned product designer from NID Ahmedabad whose clean lines and modern interpretation bring fresh life to this 80s icon. Every detail in the artwork reflects both cinematic nostalgia and contemporary design excellence.<br>Perfect for serious Mollywood collectors, 80s kids who grew up on video cassettes, and anyone who respects when a collaboration actually elevates the original. Printed on premium 100% cotton with the relaxed unisex fit Petrocrib is known for – built to last through years of wear while honouring a true cinematic legend.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Special collaboration</strong>: Petrocrib × Akash (NID Ahmedabad product designer)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Tribute to Mohanlal's iconic Sagar Alias Jacky from <em>Irupatham Noottandu</em> (1987</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Limited edition design blending 80s nostalgia with modern aesthetics</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>100% premium cotton – soft, durable, Kerala-weather ready</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Relaxed unisex fit for everyday wear or collector display</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>High-quality print that respects the collaboration's craftsmanship</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
