  "handle": "central-shree",
  "title": "Central Shree",
  "body": "<h1>Central Shree – MG Sreekumar Melody Legend Tribute Tee</h1>\n<h3>Respect to the voice of Malayalam cinema.</h3>\n<p>Some voices become the soundtrack of a generation. Central Shree is our heartfelt tribute to MG Sreekumar, the legendary playback singer whose melodic delivery and perfect diction made him the defining voice of Malayalam cinema through the 80s and 90s.</p>\n<p>Some voices become the soundtrack of a generation. Central Shree is our heartfelt tribute to MG Sreekumar, the legendary playback singer whose melodic delivery and perfect diction made him the defining voice of Malayalam cinema through the 80s and 90s.</p>\n<p>Some voices become the soundtrack of a generation. Central Shree is our heartfelt tribute to MG Sreekumar, the legendary playback singer whose melodic delivery and perfect diction made him the defining voice of Malayalam cinema through the 80s and 90s.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Respectful tribute to MG Sreekumar's legendary melodic voice</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Celebrating the singer who defined Malayalam film music</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Modern fusion with Central Cee while honoring MG Sreekumar</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>100% premium cotton – soft, breathable for Kerala weather</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Relaxed unisex fit perfect for music lovers and performers</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Designed to honor Malayalam music's greatest voice</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
