  "body": "<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div data-state=\"active\" data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"radix-:r1mr:-trigger-default\" id=\"radix-:r1mr:-content-default\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" id=\"markdown-content-2\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h1>Yeezus – Kanye West India Concert Essential Tee</h1>\n<h3>India concert ready. Yeezus lives.</h3>\n<p>This tee captures that raw Yeezus gospel-meets-hip-hop intensity for Indian Kanye fans ready to scream \"New Slang\" live. Perfect for front row, VIP sections, or just owning the afterparty. Clean minimalist design works with streetwear fits, cargos, or even your best bandh gala look.</p>\n<p>Made from premium 100% cotton with Petrocrib's relaxed unisex fit – breathable enough for sweaty mosh pits, durable for festival travel from Kochi to Kolkata. Your Yeezus statement for when Kanye finally touches down.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li><span>Built for Kanye West India concert 2026</span></li>\n<li>\n<p>Yeezus album aesthetic – minimalist, bold, Ye energy</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>100% premium cotton – sweat‑ready, festival‑durable</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Relaxed unisex fit for Indian body types and concert crowds</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Must‑have Kanye merch alternative for India tour</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div id=\"footer-portal-high\"></div>\n<div id=\"footer-portal-default\"></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div id=\"ask-input\" role=\"textbox\" spellcheck=\"true\" aria-placeholder=\"Ask a follow-up\" data-lexical-editor=\"true\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><br></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-type=\"portal\"><br></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
